## 1. Visão Geral

- **Stack:** Next.js 16.2.9 · React 19 · TypeScript · Tailwind 4 · Prisma 7 · PostgreSQL
- **Deploy:** Vercel (push → preview/production)
- **Auth:** NextAuth Credentials — bcrypt, role via JWT→session

